{"tid":133503,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個扑野被人撞破o既經歷","createTime":"2017-02-24T15:58:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-24T17:34:53.000Z","uid":1369,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ca6f61041e21ec2ee8f4b6f0700459076045668f","tid":133503,"uid":1369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T15:58:29.000Z","msg":"我先<br />\n小弟係最後一屆AL ge考生<br />\n考試咁梗係要溫書架啦<br />\n溫書梗係要係屋企溫先溫到啦<br />\n咁係條女屋企溫書就更加事半功倍 （E家已經係ex ）<br />\n<br />\n我帶齊書同埋dom，興致勃勃咁去ex屋企。<br />\n上到當然有溫書啦，咁溫到肚餓就煮野食啦<br />\nex叫我煮腸仔蛋面，但係咁啱雪櫃無曬腸，咁ex就食我個條啦<br />\n正當我地係房度激戰時，ex又好大聲，<br />\n&rdquo;叮噹&rdquo;<br />\n我地即刻著翻衫，我拎曬所有野企係房門後。<br />\nex去o左開門，係uncle黎。<br />\n點知uncle入o廁所去大<br />\n我007上身，用忍者般o既步法跳出屋企門口<br />\n就咁避過一劫<br />\n<br />\n唔知各位巴絲又有乜經歷呢"},{"pid":"9194c4848206fff0c346e807e8f552ce40b74f9a","tid":133503,"uid":1369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T16:00:52.000Z","msg":"開錯台sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10e60bcded22d16b1200d85d94ad71a3baddcb6f","tid":133503,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T16:37:59.000Z","msg":"7.7<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"019f9afce5bedfd80d2bfe62c0fa3004f4302f25","tid":133503,"uid":14744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T16:45:00.000Z","msg":"屌你老味<br />\n成撚日小妹小妹一早估撚到又係d死毒L扮女人<br />\n而家又係到刷存在感<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08754c14a60697212ef209fb6c6f1a8436b64a7b","tid":133503,"uid":29863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T16:47:27.000Z","msg":"同初瓏做愛比人撞到"},{"pid":"3b5ac6393a50193cd086261e04b47b8db1c8c46f","tid":133503,"uid"